  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;m writing this Letter to the Web in a different software than I normally use. Rather than using Emacs, an old-school text-editor on Linux, I\u0026rsquo;m using 4theWords, a browser-based word processor that has gamification features added on. For example, I currently have 24 hours, 26 minutes, and 20 seconds to write an additional 1608 words, in order to defeat something called a Mertino, as part of the game\u0026rsquo;s annual NaNoWriMo challenge.\n",
